minios-tools (1.4.2) UNRELEASED; urgency=medium

  * Update sb2iso script to version 1.5. Enhance script to support GRUB
    bootloader and improve error handling for missing files
  * Remove `minios-kernelpack`. Its functions are now performed by
    `minios-kernel` and `minios-kernel-manager`
  * Add Indonesian translation
  * Update translations

